; Regression test for issue #746: ledger convert --auto-match only matches only one posting (BZ#746)
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/746
;
; Bug: --auto-match only matched the first CSV posting; subsequent entries got Expenses:Unknown
; Fix: all postings should be matched against the existing journal using similarity search

2023/01/01 Grocery Store
    Expenses:Food    $50.00
    Assets:Checking

2023/01/15 Gas Station
    Expenses:Gas     $30.00
    Assets:Checking

test --auto-match convert $sourcepath/test/input/746.csv
2024/01/05 * Grocery Store
    Expenses:Food                                -60
    Equity:Unknown

2024/01/10 * Gas Station
    Expenses:Gas                                 -35
    Equity:Unknown

2024/01/20 * Grocery Store
    Expenses:Food                                -55
    Equity:Unknown
end test
